{"tid":2315959,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"請夏確診後首發聲「連說3次抱歉」：是我不夠小心 　公司出面闢謠","createTime":"2020-12-07T13:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T14:05:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aea02660ff8c95f0a5d1b08662991929424dfdab","tid":2315959,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:42:48.000Z","msg":"南韓疫情持續升溫，並且在演藝圈延燒開來。歌手請夏在7日宣告確診新冠肺炎（COVID-19），曾與她接觸過的TWICE Sana、宇宙少女璉靜、gu9udan美娜、DIA鄭彩娟，以及各團的團員也都透過所屬經紀公司透露已接受採檢、正在進行自主隔離。而請夏在確診消息發布後，為了不讓粉絲擔心，也親自在Fan Cafe發聲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5320/d5320005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5320%2Fd5320005.jpg&h=48fa2579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲請夏確診。（圖／翻攝請夏官方IG）<br />\n<br />\n請夏在文中寫下：「怕我們BYULHARANG（별하랑，請夏粉絲名）會因為都沒消息而擔心，所以寫下這篇文，非常對不起、非常抱歉，明明很小心了，看來是我做的還不足。」向粉絲致歉，透露自己也是在今天（7日）接收到通知，才知道自己確診，並且承諾會盡快以健康的模樣回歸，最後則是再度強調「BYULHARANG也要小心，不要太擔心我，很快可以見面的，再次向大家道歉」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5320/d5320007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5320%2Fd5320007.jpg&h=0adf2204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲請夏在官咖發聲，向粉絲致歉並希望粉絲不要擔心。（圖／翻攝請夏官方IG）<br />\n<br />\n此外，在請夏確診後，韓網上也流傳著各式各樣的不實消息，對此，所屬公司MNH娛樂再次發出聲明解釋，表示請夏先前為了肩膀的舊傷，曾在12月2日至首爾某體育中心進行復健，之後5日被告知該處出現了確診者，而當時請夏方面雖未接收到檢測的通知，但公司為了保險起見，依然讓請夏接受了檢測，並得到了陽性結果。<br />\n<br />\nMNH娛樂也強烈警告：「請不要散播未經過確認的不實消息。」並透露政府防疫部門正在調查中，準確的感染路線會在調查結果出爐後公佈，也承諾會積極配合政府的指示，採取相關措施。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5320/5320008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5320%2F5320008.jpg&h=68acff12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"236d2d4deeb89b7ccf6be710fcbeb3c0d247eccc","tid":2315959,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:43:50.000Z","msg":"最衰都係武漢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ba232e2fd17c8ed53df40931b8ede8e0da50dd","tid":2315959,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"哭𠹌咗....."},{"pid":"94ac216321d36a6f41a7ef436770eccc6c45243c","tid":2315959,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"我老公wood千奇唔好有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c78ec19544e784c0c85c06d2719704b9007f1e","tid":2315959,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:44:46.000Z","msg":"請夏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6593dc170f042b5fe7c5a39751b2c247a7835d7a","tid":2315959,"uid":8795,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"牙酒唔好再道歉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c5244394f6a6e3922845f19af83751d19e94d1","tid":2315959,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"94ac216321d36a6f41a7ef436770eccc6c45243c","tid":2315959,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"我老公wood千奇唔好有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" c